b7f142c8-2fd2-45df-8476-8628d45f5c07.title: Doric
b7f142c8-2fd2-45df-8476-8628d45f5c07.text: Hello traveller, what brings you to my humble smithy?

options.text: 遰 I wanted to use your anvils.
I want to use your whetstone.
I was just checking out the landscape.

74da88d4-4e3a-450e-969e-fc61404f26c3.title: <player>
74da88d4-4e3a-450e-969e-fc61404f26c3.text: I wanted to use your anvils.

f3dec5ea-b7d6-45bd-bbca-7a7d3e32ec06.title: Doric
f3dec5ea-b7d6-45bd-bbca-7a7d3e32ec06.text:
My anvils get enough work with my own use. I make
pickaxes, and it takes a lot of hard work. If you could
get me some more materials, then I could let you use
them.

options.text: 遰 Yes, I will get you the materials.
No, hitting rocks is for the boring people, sorry.

83f628fe-9593-458e-a55b-a54b647226ea.title: <player>
83f628fe-9593-458e-a55b-a54b647226ea.text: I wanted to use your whetstone.

46d04e9b-ab9a-4187-97d6-09bc53e078eb.title: Doric
46d04e9b-ab9a-4187-97d6-09bc53e078eb.text:
The whetstone is for more advanced smithing, but I
could let you use it as well as my anvils if you could
get me some more materials.

f3e3f0d5-6187-45fe-9110-60e73d7d0dbb.title: Doric
f3e3f0d5-6187-45fe-9110-60e73d7d0dbb.text:
How nice to meet someone with such pleasant manners.
Do come again when you need to shout at someone
smaller than you!

4fea321f-837c-464d-910c-18cdb5847f8a.title: <player>
4fea321f-837c-464d-910c-18cdb5847f8a.text: I was just checking out the landscape.

9c55bd71-608a-41e3-9259-7c1cf3d989da.title: Doric
9c55bd71-608a-41e3-9259-7c1cf3d989da.text:
Hope you like it. I do enjoy the solitude of my little
home. If you get time, please say hi to my friends in
the Dwarven Mine.

46f67685-7b58-4469-98ea-1b3e2dd4e21c.title: Doric
46f67685-7b58-4469-98ea-1b3e2dd4e21c.text:
Yep, the entrance is in the side of Ice Mountain just to
the east of here. They're a friendly bunch. Stop in at
Nurmof's store and buy one of my pickaxes!

aeb6cef8-1c73-494f-92f1-c8d6b56a1029.title: Doric
aeb6cef8-1c73-494f-92f1-c8d6b56a1029.text:
I make pickaxes. I am the best maker of pickaxes in the
whole of Gielinor.

a687b449-9f3a-41c5-aa66-519092dfd760.title: <player>
a687b449-9f3a-41c5-aa66-519092dfd760.text: Do you have any to sell?

ae70637e-4fde-4f4e-be43-83d023ef378d.title: Doric
ae70637e-4fde-4f4e-be43-83d023ef378d.text: Sorry, but I've got a running order with Nurmof.

2480da70-9bd9-43cb-81d0-d3c852aa8464.title: Doric
2480da70-9bd9-43cb-81d0-d3c852aa8464.text:
Nurmof has a store over in the Dwarven Mine. You
can find the entrance on the side of Ice Mountain to
the east of here.

7c5cdce3-03e1-431e-b650-2e6298d2cceb.title: <player>
7c5cdce3-03e1-431e-b650-2e6298d2cceb.text: No, hitting rocks is for the boring people, sorry.

fe18cb56-e77a-4445-82ed-c5248354d1f4.title: Doric
fe18cb56-e77a-4445-82ed-c5248354d1f4.text: That is your choice. Nice to meet you anyway.

ad98954c-6dfe-4079-bf7b-39830fee58be.title: <player>
ad98954c-6dfe-4079-bf7b-39830fee58be.text: Yes, I will get you the materials.

3d12a781-963a-44f3-b08f-bda7e079a1a2.title: Doric
3d12a781-963a-44f3-b08f-bda7e079a1a2.text:
Clay is what I use more than anything, to make casts.
Could you get me 6 clay, 4 copper ore, and 2 iron ore,
please? I could pay a little, and let you use my anvils.
Take this pickaxe with you just in case you need it.

17e43b7a-d9da-492c-89ff-bf7f773f6387.title: Doric
17e43b7a-d9da-492c-89ff-bf7f773f6387.text:
You'll be able to find all those ores in the rocks just
inside the Dwarven Mine. Head east from here and
you'll find the entrance in the side of Ice Mountain.

62471831-08b7-4ca8-9f66-94fac3bcca58.title: <player>
62471831-08b7-4ca8-9f66-94fac3bcca58.text: But I'm not a good enough miner to get iron ore.

12d0d80b-064a-4791-990b-a04da3941c75.title: <player>
12d0d80b-064a-4791-990b-a04da3941c75.text:
Oh well, you could practice mining until you can. Can't
beat a bit of mining - it's a useful skill. Failing that, you
might be able to find a more experienced adventurer to
buy the iron ore off.

295c3ef9-7d8d-4119-87c0-eab7f54362fb.title: Note
295c3ef9-7d8d-4119-87c0-eab7f54362fb.text: Dialogue might be dif for ironmen?

823e7194-f555-4db7-82d1-463a608e7264.title: <player>
823e7194-f555-4db7-82d1-463a608e7264.text:
You know, it's funny you should require those exact
things!

e659d7ac-a719-4e5a-b19f-95b842abea1f.title: <player>
e659d7ac-a719-4e5a-b19f-95b842abea1f.text:
I can usually fit 26 things in my backpack and in a
world full of quite literally limitless possibilities, a complete
coincidence has occurred!

590749ce-6160-4f63-8ede-dc7c1e57ecc9.title: Doric
590749ce-6160-4f63-8ede-dc7c1e57ecc9.text: I don't quite understand what you're saying?

e2fed25a-2584-4219-8894-45023f0b5d74.title: <player>
e2fed25a-2584-4219-8894-45023f0b5d74.text:
Well, out of pure coincidence, despite definitely not
knowing what you were about to request, I just so
happened to have carried those exact items!

0c251421-54ce-42f9-9d75-4c053aa65844.title: <player>
0c251421-54ce-42f9-9d75-4c053aa65844.text: In fact, in the exact quantities too!

7f149343-730c-4a37-84fd-73cc264721a6.title: Doric
7f149343-730c-4a37-84fd-73cc264721a6.text:
Oh my, that is a coincidence! Pass them here, please. I
can spare you some coins for your trouble, and please
use my anvils any time you want.

71c4bedb-6c14-4527-ad70-0ac82b68a73b.text: You hand the clay, copper, and iron to Doric.

8bb5e653-6dae-4bc0-97f9-52d30e7bbb8e.title: Doric
8bb5e653-6dae-4bc0-97f9-52d30e7bbb8e.text:
You'll be able to find all those ores in the rocks just
inside the Dwarven Mine. Head east from here and
you'll find the entrance in the side of Ice Mountain.

cef6b69f-dd72-4395-8834-0c94b8f22952.title: <player>
cef6b69f-dd72-4395-8834-0c94b8f22952.text: But I'm not a good enough miner to get iron ore.

cb1c2ea8-f118-410f-9123-a77090993ebf.title: <player>
cb1c2ea8-f118-410f-9123-a77090993ebf.text:
Oh well, you could practice mining until you can. Can't
beat a bit of mining - it's a useful skill. Failing that, you
might be able to find a more experienced adventurer to
buy the iron ore off.

89d111b9-9092-48f4-b5e0-95235425d992.title: Note
89d111b9-9092-48f4-b5e0-95235425d992.text: Dialogue might be dif for ironmen?

397ecec4-cbe9-4e96-8c6d-0ad64ad6b403.title: Doric
397ecec4-cbe9-4e96-8c6d-0ad64ad6b403.text: Have you got my materials yet, traveller?

ee591441-1c8e-483f-a7da-6f9e343514af.title: <player>
ee591441-1c8e-483f-a7da-6f9e343514af.text: Sorry, I don't have them all yet.

d19d8258-9262-4db2-90fd-dc7be6415c99.title: Doric
d19d8258-9262-4db2-90fd-dc7be6415c99.text:
Not to worry, stick at it. Remember, I need 6 clay, 4
copper ore, and 2 iron ore.

a45cc24d-4240-4eab-b14b-a6efab75364e.title: Doric
a45cc24d-4240-4eab-b14b-a6efab75364e.text:
Many thanks! Pass them here, please. I can spare you
some coins for your trouble, and please use my anvils
any time you want.

fc17b2c5-f800-4964-ad86-15fdce43f561.text: You hand the clay, copper, and iron to Doric.

6652d6b8-7404-46cb-8408-586d019cd0bb.title: Doric
6652d6b8-7404-46cb-8408-586d019cd0bb.text: Hello traveller, how is your metalworking coming along?

1ee63f16-e1c2-4f61-90af-8bea25f71942.title: Doric
1ee63f16-e1c2-4f61-90af-8bea25f71942.text: Good, the love of metal is a thing close to my heart.
